tandard rather than around a human foot.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>A boot that weighs 460 grams and flexes like a trainer doesn't just reduce fatigue from the weight. It stops fighting your foot all day long. The blisters ease. The ankle stiffness goes. The feet that were done by lunchtime start making it to the end of the shift in one piece.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The concrete isn't going anywhere. But what you put on your feet before you step onto it is entirely your choice.</p>"}],
